### 결제 처리 (잔액 전액 차감)
POST http://localhost:8888/api/v1/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "userId": 1
}

###

### 결제 처리 (복합 결제 - 잔액 + 포인트 + 쿠폰 할인)
POST http://localhost:8888/api/v1/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "breakdown": {
    "balanceAmount": 8000,
    "pointAmount": 1000,
    "cardAmount": 0,
    "couponDiscount": 1000
  }
}
